  "body": "For bft migration create a sub-protocol configuration and protocol manager that allows the sub-protocol messages to reach the specific consensus mechanisms protocol manager according to the consensus mechanism migration schedule.\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**\n* All the underlying capabilities from the migrating consensus mechanism will need to be listed in a combined protocol configuration as Besu doesn't currently allow changing this at runtime\n* Each protocol manager will need to be wrapped in a switchable protocol manager for each subprotocol. So that eth messages for example will go to ibft2 whilst ibft2 is being used and then switch to the qbft protocol manager when the qbft block height is reached.",
